        <p>We're sorry, but the online service for creating a lasting power of attorney (LPA) is undergoing essential maintenance. It will be available again shortly.</p>

        <p>If you have any questions, you can call the Office of the Public Guardian's contact centre: </p>

        <p>
            <strong class="bold">0300 456 0300</strong>
        </p>

        <p>Lines are open Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm (except Wednesday, 10am to 5pm). </p>

        <p>If you'd like to know more about LPAs and other ways to make them, <a href="https://www.gov.uk/power-of-attorney">this guide provides a simple, up-to-date introduction</a>. </p>

